#### 5.2 Smart Property Matching Engine
```js
// POST /api/properties/match — AI-powered recommendation
const { budget, location, purpose, size } = req.body;
// Use pgvector extension for embedding-based similarity search
const embedding = await openai.embeddings.create({
  model: 'text-embedding-3-small',
  input: `${purpose} property in ${location} budget ${budget} size ${size}`,
});
const matches = await query(
  `SELECT *, 1 - (embedding <=> $1) as similarity 
   FROM properties WHERE is_active = TRUE
   ORDER BY similarity DESC LIMIT 10`,
  [`[${embedding.data[0].embedding}]`]
);
```
Install `pgvector` PostgreSQL extension. Store property embeddings when creating/updating listings. **This is the feature that 10x's your conversion rate.**

#### 5.3 Automated Arabic/English Content Translation
Your i18n is currently manual JSON files. Add auto-translation for DB content:
```js
// services/translate.service.js
const translateContent = async (text, targetLang) => {
  const response = await openai.chat.completions.create({
    model: 'gpt-4o-mini',
